sql:
SELECT MAX(score) AS highest_score
FROM user_progress
WHERE level_id = 0;

SELECT invasion_date
FROM invasions
WHERE destruction_level > 20;

SELECT monster_name
FROM monsters
ORDER BY strength DESC;

SELECT SUM(score) AS total_score, AVG(score) AS average_score
FROM user_progress
WHERE user_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
The hierarchy of invasions refers to the sequence of invasions that have occurred in each city over time, with each invasion potentially causing increased destruction; 
The total destruction level of a city refers to the cumulative destruction caused by all invasions in that city;
The total score of a user refers to the sum of scores earned by the user for completing all levels featuring invasions.

